                            <comment id="14212088" author="aash" created="Fri, 14 Nov 2014 10:12:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t see a &lt;tt&gt;ClusterScheduler&lt;/tt&gt; class on master &amp;#8211; was that refactored to &lt;tt&gt;TaskSchedulerImpl&lt;/tt&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There is still a &lt;tt&gt;Thread.sleep(1000)&lt;/tt&gt; in that class&apos;s &lt;tt&gt;stop()&lt;/tt&gt; though, which may be what this ticket refers to: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/1df05a40ebf3493b0aff46d18c0f30d2d5256c7b/core/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/scheduler/TaskSchedulerImpl.scala#L399&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/1df05a40ebf3493b0aff46d18c0f30d2d5256c7b/core/src/main/scala/org/apache/spark/scheduler/TaskSchedulerImpl.scala#L399&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
